description:
Do you want to be a part of our growing team and experience an enjoyable working environment while enhancing your professional skills for career advancement?

As the company’s  
MARKETING SUPERVISOR, you are:

o Responsible for the development and implementation of marketing programs;  
o Develop the marketing plans and programs in alignment with the company’s overall goal;  
o Does extensive and intensive research relevant to promotions and events  
o Prepares yearly promotional programs and coordinates closely with the Operations / Sales Department regarding its details for further evaluation and feedback;  
o Cascades program to the stores including the timely delivery of the needed materials;  
Keeps an eye on the output and performance of the marketing assistants, Online Staff, and Operation staff;  
o Responsible for the planning, directing, and coordinating the marketing activities of the company;  
o Promote and raise brand awareness ;  
o Supervises, trains, and coaches Operations Staff, Marketing, and Online Staff;  
o Create strong social media communication ideas and effective media plans in coordination with concerned departments and advertising/PR agencies, as applicable, and ensure  
implementation as planned;  
o Adopts technology to develop, implement, track, and optimize digital marketing campaigns and social media across all channels.

To be a MARKETING  
SUPERVISOR, you must be:  
o Graduate of BS Marketing or any equivalent;  
o Has at least 3 years of experience in the field of marketing;  
o At least 2-3 years (s) of working experience handling marketing of a retail company or any related industry;  
o Adept in social media, brand posting and trade marketing;  
o Outstanding people management, communication and technical skills;  
o Capability to work under pressure

**BENEFITS & OTHERS:**  
Competitive Salary  
Monthly Incentive  
Load Allowance  
Food Allowance  
Travel Allowance  
Health Insurance  
Government Statutory  
Benefits  
Leave Credits

Job Type: Full-time

Pay: Php25,000.00 - Php30,000.00 per month

Schedule:

* 8 hour shift

Supplemental pay types:

* 13th month salary
* Overtime pay

Expected Start Date: 06/30/2024
